text: Wildsville is an unincorporated community in Concordia Parish, Louisiana, United States. The community is located on U.S. Route 84, east of Jonesville. Wildsville had a post office until May 13, 1995; it still has its own ZIP code, 71377. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Concordia Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
